Nigeria’s popular singer Ayodeji Balogun popularly known as Wizkid has declared his intention to venture into prostitution business, popularly known as ‘Ashawo’. Wizkid made the comment on while responding to fellow singer, Teni’s question on the kind of business he would love to establish. “Which business do you need money to start? I’ll pick three people. #Billionaire. I’ll be picking three people that need help starting their business”, Teni wrote on her INstagram page. Wizkid who appeared to be joking commented saying “Ashawo business, Please help us billionaire.” See below: 